can_not_create_asset_from_symbol_master.en: Can't create asset from symbol master.

slice_must_in_group.en: Slice layer must in side a group.

color_xml_from_layers.zh: 选中图层的色彩 XML 资源

color_xml_from_color_variables.zh: 色彩变量的 XML 资源

not_support_layer_style.en: Layer style like shadow and blur is not support by Android shape drawable.
not_support_layer_style.zh: Android 形状资源不支持投影、模糊等图层样式。

too_many_color_stop.en: The gradient in Android shape drawable not support greater than 3 colors.
too_many_color_stop.zh: Android 形状资源不支持大于 3 种颜色的渐变。

no_support_fill_type.en: The fill type is not support for Android shape drawable.
no_support_fill_type.zh: Android 形状资源不支持图像等填充类型。

no_support_stroke_type.en: The stroke type is not support for Android shape drawable.
no_support_stroke_type.zh: Android 形状资源不支持渐变、图像等描边类型。

no_support_shape.en: Only support shape layer like rectangle or oval.
no_support_shape.zh: Android 形状资源只支持矩形、圆等形状。

no_shape_layer.en: Please choose 1 shape layer like rectangle or oval.
no_shape_layer.zh: 请选择一个矩形、圆等形状图层。

description.en: Export Android resources in Sketch. Support bitmap, vector, nine-patch, app icon, shape XML and color.
description.zh: 用于导出 Android 各种资源的 Sketch 插件，支持位图、矢量、点九、应用图标、形状 XML 和色彩 XML。

can_not_create_nine_patch_from_artboard_.en: Can't create Nine-Patch from Artboard or Symbol Master.
can_not_create_nine_patch_from_artboard_.zh: 不可从画板或组件模版创建点九资源。

asset_name_type_0.en: Valid last part of layer name. (a / b / c -> c)
asset_name_type_0.zh: 合法的最后段图层名. (a / b / c -> c)

asset_name_type_1.en: Valid full layer name. (a / b / c -> a_b_c)
asset_name_type_1.zh: 合法的完整图层名. (a / b / c -> a_b_c)

asset_name_type_2.en: Last part of layer name. (a / b / c -> c)
asset_name_type_2.zh: 最后段图层名. (a / b / c -> c)

asset_name_type_3.en: Full layer name. (a / b / c -> a_b_c)
asset_name_type_3.zh: 完整图层名. (a / b / c -> a_b_c)

show_in_finder_after_export.zh: 导出资源后在 Finder 中显示。

least_export_dpis.en: At least keep 1 export dpi is checked.
least_export_dpis.zh: 导出分辨率选项必须至少保留一项。

current_page_is_no_template.en: Current page is no a Android app icon template.
current_page_is_no_template.zh: 当前页不是一个 Android 应用图标模版。

app_icon_not_find.en: Can't find Android app icon inside current page.
app_icon_not_find.zh: 在当前页中找不到 Android 应用图标。

cannot_export_to_folder.en: You can't export assets to this folder.
cannot_export_to_folder.zh: 无法导入文件到此文件夹。

nine_patch_layer_structure_is_wrong.en: The layer structure of nine-patch asset is wrong.
nine_patch_layer_structure_is_wrong.zh: 点九资源的图层结构有误。

no_selected_shape_layer.en: Please select at least 1 shape layer with solid or gradient fill.
no_selected_shape_layer.zh: 请选中至少一个带有单色或渐变填充的图层。

no_color_in_selected_layers.en: No any color in selected layer.
no_color_in_selected_layers.zh: 选中的图层中没有任何颜色。

ga_disable.zh: 禁用 “谷歌分析” 跟踪用户数据。

ga_tip.en: This plugin use Google Analytics for tacking user area, language and plugin action, that used to help improve plugin. You can "Disagree" to disable it.
ga_tip.zh: 插件使用 “谷歌分析” 跟踪用户国家地区、语言及插件执行动作等信息用于改进插件体验，点击 “不同意” 禁用分析功能不会影响插件使用。

vector_drawable_precision.en: Precision of pathData in Vector Drawable
vector_drawable_precision.zh: 矢量资源路径数据小数精度
